-- what is the diff b/w a Filter and an Interceptor, when should
you use each?

filters and interceptors both of them allow the requests before and
after they reach controllers.
But they work at diff levels 

filter operates at servlet level before the request enters into
springframework
-it intercepts the request before they reach dispatcher servlet.
- Interceptor operates at spring level that after request maps to a controller.
it works after dispatcherServlet and before the controller.
